lead_paragraph: Brandon Belt was a homer short of the cycle and drove in five runs, Hunter Pence drove in a pair on three hits and the San Francisco Giants completed a three-game sweep by beating the San Diego Padres 13-9 on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Belt Drives in 5, Giants Complete Sweep of Padres
